node.text:
We all have to start▶️ somewhere.
.
I started 2 years ago, low⬇️ confidence, scared😖 of public speaking. The reason why I decided to become an instructor🚴‍♀️ was to overcome performance anxiety.
.
I took baby👼 steps, pushed myself, and came in consistently.
.
I had to give myself credit💯 for how far I have come and my hard work translated into noticeable improvement on myself.
.
⚠️So, don’t be afraid to step out of your comfort zone and try something new. If I can do it, you can too 🤩 
#mondaymotivation
找到自己的使命感,是最爽的 🔥
Amazing!  Thanks for sharing! I’m super proud of you!!!

Well said, and it's true. Convincing yourself to start is definitely the hardest part. 
Fantastic job though. Not everybody can say they've achieved what you have. It takes real determination and courage.
